      "id": 146859622,
      "body": "This post really got my attention!\n\nI\u2019ve run into the same issue, wherein I\u2019m studying an advanced text and many of the most important proofs have assumptions stated by the author to be obvious. I would also lose confidence at that point. Being stubborn is the only way I\u2019ve gotten through these texts, and reaching out to others has also helped.\n\nOn the other hand, I have become very skeptical when reaching out because I\u2019ve run into work and advice that was wrong, but again it wasn\u2019t always obviously so. At these times, I wish I would have had a connection with a reputable mathematician! I\u2019ve often spent considerable time trying to figure out something \u201cobvious\u201d on my own, sometimes abandoning the problem for long periods of time.",
